&nbsp;In the video, the 41-year-old man is tied to a post by his genitals, beaten with sticks and kicked continuously to the chants of onlookers, with community members claiming he had been caught assaulting the girl.At the time police found no charges against him but continued to investigate the matter. Yesterday, police spokesperson Andr Traut confirmed a complaint of sexual assault had been lodged against the man. A case of sexual assault of a 9-year-old girl has been reported and the suspect, a 41-year-old male, has been arrested. He is currently detained in hospital under police guard, due to the injuries sustained when he was assaulted by community members, said Traut.Read full story: http://www.dailyvoice.co.za/news/sex-offender-beaten-in-viral-video-bust/